{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d2baddac36","title":"致上海黄苗夫函","origin":"根据文件翻印件打印。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5da11a9261","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":25,"articleId":"d2baddac36"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"3f07c9dd47","name":"中国民主建国会"},{"id":"8828f25077","name":"章乃器"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"549669b95b","type":"title","text":"致上海黄苗夫函","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d2baddac36"},{"id":"ef36d0128d","type":"authors","text":"中国民主建国会章乃器","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d2baddac36"},{"id":"1d5bbe3d0d","type":"subtitle","text":"（章乃器：国务院粮食部部长，民主建国会副主任委员）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d2baddac36"},{"id":"9394022e49","type":"paragraph","text":"黄苗夫同志：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d2baddac36"},{"id":"0b3e6caba4","type":"paragraph","text":"两次鸣文，都详细读了，十分同情你的遭遇，全力支持你彻底地鸣，彻底地放，这正是对于党的方针的信任，党希望大家这样做，如党中央的指示所说的，有少数党员像国民党，这些人如不彻底改造，对人民国家和党都是不利的，所以帮助整风，就是爱党爱国家，爱人民，要用“团结——批评——团结”的方式，把整风运动进行到底，将来如有人敢对于你打击报复，我一定尽绵薄为你撑腰。一般说来，错误是怕太阳的，所以，揭发总比不揭发好，但也不能认为一次整风就把歪风全部整掉了，企图乘机报复的人，还是会有的，但绝不可怕，致敬礼!","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d2baddac36"},{"id":"71f6fe95d2","type":"paragraph","text":" 章乃器  五·二十五","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d2baddac36"}],"page":{"id":"bda1a122e1","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d2baddac36","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}